text:
We are currently in pilot phase (toggle switch for certain people). A lot of
cosmetic changes, but a few issues. The Teams outlook add-in didn’t load on a
few after the switch and the date on a teams message is in US format, we are in
Australia. We are probably going to go live in the next month or so I would
think 
Still a few other known issues Known issues in the new Microsoft Teams desktop
client - Microsoft Teams | Microsoft Learn
